#. HTML: <section class="sutta" id="sn29.10"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn29.10:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 29 "
msgstr "Linked Discourses 29 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn29.10:0.2"
msgid "1. Nāgavagga "
msgstr "1. Dragons "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
#. VAR: 10. Catutthasutasutta → tassa sutam 4 (pts1)
msgctxt "sn29.10:0.3"
msgid "10. Catutthasutasutta "
msgstr "10. They’ve Heard (4th) "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: sc1
msgctxt "sn29.10:1.1"
msgid "Sāvatthinidānaṃ. "
msgstr "At Sāvatthī. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn29.10:1.2"
msgid "Ekamantaṃ nisinno kho so bhikkhu bhagavantaṃ etadavoca: "
msgstr "Seated to one side, that mendicant said to the Buddha: "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn29.10:1.3"
msgid "“ko nu kho, bhante, hetu, ko paccayo, yena midhekacco kāyassa bhedā paraṃ maraṇā opapātikānaṃ nāgānaṃ sahabyataṃ upapajjatī”ti? "
msgstr "“Sir, what is the cause, what is the reason why someone, when their body breaks up, after death, is reborn in the company of the spontaneously-born dragons?” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc2
msgctxt "sn29.10:2.1"
msgid "“Idha, bhikkhu, ekacco kāyena dvayakārī hoti, vācāya dvayakārī, manasā dvayakārī. "
msgstr "(All should be told in full.) "

msgctxt "sn29.10:2.2"
msgid "Tassa sutaṃ hoti: "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "sn29.10:2.3"
msgid "‘opapātikā nāgā dīghāyukā vaṇṇavanto sukhabahulā’ti. "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "sn29.10:2.4"
msgid "Tassa evaṃ hoti: "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "sn29.10:2.5"
msgid "‘aho vatāhaṃ kāyassa bhedā paraṃ maraṇā opapātikānaṃ nāgānaṃ sahabyataṃ upapajjeyyan’ti. "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "sn29.10:2.6"
msgid "So kāyassa bhedā paraṃ maraṇā opapātikānaṃ nāgānaṃ sahabyataṃ upapajjati. "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "sn29.10:2.7"
msgid "Ayaṃ kho, bhikkhu, hetu, ayaṃ paccayo, yena midhekacco kāyassa bhedā paraṃ maraṇā opapātikānaṃ nāgānaṃ sahabyataṃ upapajjatī”ti. "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn29.10:2.8"
msgid "Dasamaṃ. "
msgstr ""

